  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Assessment of optic disc morphology can be difficult in patients with uveitis and
      papilloedema. Therefore different optical coherence tomography (OCT) and laser scanning
      techniques may help to detect damage to the retinal nerve fibre layer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
